<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-11-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-11-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="710" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d710">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00116 PW/11–1945:
                                    Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Acting Political Adviser in Japan</hi>
                                        (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Atcheson</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-11-19">November 19,
                                            1945</date>.<lb/>[Received November 19—11:40
                                        a.m.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>147. Orders were issued by the Supreme Commander to the Japanese
                                    Government under date of November 17 to effect the arrest of
                                    persons listed in our 121, November 13<note n="6" xml:id="d710fn1">Not printed, but see despatch 52, November
                                        13, <ref target="#pg_961">p. 961</ref>.</note> except
                                    Itagaki and Yamada who are understood to be out of the country.
                                    According to press, Matsuoka recently attempted suicide.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Atcheson</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>